This paper deals with data warehousing and multidimensional data, which are typically studied in the database (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new operator for multidimensional queries, which could fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper presents experiments on large data sets, which could be of interest to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
